manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "pwnhub-bot"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "pwnhub-bot"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1"
async-trait = "0.1"
serde_with = "2"
tracing-log = "0.1"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.figment]
version = "0.10"
features = ["env", "toml"]
optional = false

[dependencies.poise]
version = "0.3"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.secrecy]
version = "0.8"
features = ["serde"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serenity]
version = "0.11"
features = ["builder", "cache", "collector", "client", "gateway", "http", "model", "tokio_task_builder", "rustls_backend"]
optional = false
default-features = false

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.6"
features = ["postgres", "chrono", "runtime-tokio-rustls", "uuid", "tls", "offline", "macros"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.20"
features = ["full"]
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = []
optional = false
